 _______________________________________________________________________

 Mandriva Linux Security Advisory                         MDVSA-2013:033
 http://www.mandriva.com/en/support/security/
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Package : cronie
 Date    : April 5, 2013
 Affected: Business Server 1.0
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Problem Description:

 Updated cronie package fixes the following issue:
 
 It was reported that cronie 1.4.8 would leak certain file
 descriptors. On systems where /etc/crontab is not world-readable this
 could be an information disclosure concern (CVE-2012-6097).
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:

 http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2012-6097
 https://wiki.mageia.org/en/Support/Advisories/MGASA-2013-0023
 _______________________________________________________________________

